data.description:
Conveniently located just minutes from restaurants and a variety of lakes and parks, this Crystal home is ready for a new owner!

Pulling up, you'll notice the huge attached garage and an oversized front porch. Inside, you're greeted by a cozy living room with an abundance of natural light, stunning wood floors, and a fireplace.

Around the corner is the large, eat-in kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances and plenty of room for meal prep and storage.

The primary suite comes complete with a full bathroom with double vanities and a tub! An additional fireplace can also be found in the garage.

Outdoor gatherings are best held on the spacious back deck overlooking the expansive, fenced-in yard.

Schedule your own VIP showing today!
